virtue.name: Charity
virtue.description: Charity has its rewards.

virtue.name: Compassion
virtue.description: Your compassion is one of your greatest strengths.

virtue.name: Confidence
virtue.description: Your actions have instilled in you a great sense of confidence.

virtue.name: Determination
virtue.description: Your determination has won you many victories.

virtue.name: Discipline
virtue.description: The discipline you maintain makes you stronger in the face of danger.

virtue.name: Empathy
virtue.description: You have a proven empathy for those in need.

virtue.name: Fidelity
virtue.description: Your fidelity has earned you the respect of those around you.

virtue.name: Fortitude
virtue.description: Your struggles have built in you tremendous fortitude.

virtue.name: Honesty
virtue.description: Your honesty has earned you the trust of those around you and the fear of your enemies.

virtue.name: Honour
virtue.description: Your honour is without peer.

virtue.name: Idealism
virtue.description: Your idealism can brook no fault.

virtue.name: Innocence
virtue.description: Your innocence can be used as a shield.

virtue.name: Justice
virtue.description: You are a servant of justice.

virtue.name: Loyalty
virtue.description: Your loyalty shall be rewarded.

virtue.name: Mercy
virtue.description: You have learned the value of mercy.

virtue.name: Patience
virtue.description: Patience is a virtue.

virtue.name: Tolerance
virtue.description: Your tolerance of others has taught you to shrug off much.

virtue.name: Valour
virtue.description: No one can ever question your valour.

virtue.name: Wisdom
virtue.description: You have found true wisdom.

virtue.name: Wit
virtue.description: Your well-honed wit is a true advantage.

virtue.name: Zeal
virtue.description: Your zeal drives you to perfection.
